text: Bismillapur is a town located in the Punjab province of Pakistan. It is located in Faisalabad District at 31°17'0N 73°3'0E with an altitude of 168 metres (554 feet) and lies near to the city of Lahore.Location of Bismillapur - Falling Rain Genomics Neighbouring settlements include Bilochwala to the east and Rodasar to the north. ==References== Category:Populated places in Faisalabad District
title: Bismillapur
